attentions.cn: 推荐版适用于普通版,1S不可刷
attentions.en: All Suggested Edition is not compatible with 1S model.

attentions.cn: 开发版：普通版通用，电信版可刷2.3.16及后续，青春版可刷2.5.18及后续，1S可刷2.8.24及后续，1S青春版可刷2.10.26及后续
attentions.en: China Beta: for China Telecom Devices please use 2.3.16 and further versions; Mi 1 Lite Devices please use 2.5.18 and further versions; Mi 1S Devices please use 2.8.24 and further version; Mi 1S Lite device please use 2.10.26 and further versions.

attentions.cn: 稳定版：适用于大部分小米1系列,青春版可刷ICS3.0及后续，1S可刷ICS13.0及后续，1S青春版可刷ICS19.0及后续
attentions.en: Stable ROMS：Mi 1 Lite devices user ICS3.0 and further versions; Mi 1S Devices please use ICS13.0 abd further versions; Mi 1S Lite devices please use ICS19.0 and further versions.

attentions.cn: 原生安卓：适用于大部分小米1系列,青春版可刷QDR65及后续，1S可刷QDR66及后续
attentions.en: Stock Android：Mi 1 Lite devices please use QDR65 and further; Mi 1S Devices please use QDR66 and further.
